@KepingPan Currently, the learning progress is about 0.064 for the AP from iter=430,000. Although the results are not so good, it seems that tuning should be performed on the stride of the target image or on the cpm, init, refinement stage, etc.
As you can see by outputting the target heatmap, there is a clear difference between when the stride is 8 and 16.
Thank you @Daniil-Osokin for your help.
